channel.title: Spacejam Dodian Remake!
channel.description:
Spacejam is a new Dodian remake that is here to stay!
Has all the same bosses dodian had back in the days, I will add pics etc at a later date, just doing this quickly before heading to bed as it's 3am :P
Ip is spacejam.no-ip.org
- Drop parties at player milestones to release rares - Other events to come - Looking for moderators
For a client, please use either of the Webbers clients :) You can find them by googling "webbers client" fairly easily.
See you there friends!
